Presentation.KeyConsiderations:
Services models are specified using the OMG SoaML standard&nbsp;which is an UML profile for services modeling providing a
metamodel an stereotypes specifc for services.For this activity the SoaML Services Architecture diagram has to be modeled
using some UML tool that also provides the profile (Cameo SOA+&nbsp;Magic Draw, Modelio, etc.).&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
